   "author_association" : "MEMBER",
   "body" : "This issue tracks removing the wallet 'account' API. See issue #3816 for the reasons why this is a good idea. Rather than extend that very old and long issu, I'm opening this to track concrete actions to fully remove the 'account' API.\r\n\r\nActions are:\r\n\r\n- [x] Rename account to label where appropriate (#11536)\r\n- [x] Introduce 'label' API for wallet (~#7729~ #12892)\r\n- [ ] (V0.17) Mark 'account' API as deprecated. Wallet functional tests are updated to use `-deprecatedrpc=accounts` to maintain existing behaviour.\r\n- [ ] Remove `getlabeladdress` RPC method. Keeping this method means we need to keep the `CAccount` internal accounting.\r\n- [ ] Migrate wallet functional tests to use the 'label' API.\r\n- [ ] (V0.18) Fully remove the 'account' API",
